      "link": "https://www.mountainproject.com/route/202957630/free-will",
      "pubDate": "2026-05-11T16:30:55.000Z",
      "description": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><p>Colin Bauer quietly FA'd this monstrosity on 9/9/23</p><p>Start as per \"Freedom Fries\" but stay left of the Fulgora crack, climbing straight up into and joining \"Will to Live\" to finish the line. Way to go Colin!</p></div><br /><img  class=\"\" src='' alt=\"\"><br><a href=\"https://www.mountainproject.com/area/105852400/virginia\">Virginia</a>\n        \n             &gt; <a href=\"https://www.mountainproject.com/area/110848199/southwest-virginia-appalachia\">Southwest Virgi&hellip;</a>\n        \n             &gt; <a href=\"https://www.mountainproject.com/area/106477419/grayson-highlands-state-park\">Grayson Highlan&hellip;</a>\n        \n             &gt; <a href=\"https://www.mountainproject.com/area/106521343/picnic-area\">Picnic Area</a>\n        \n             &gt; <a href=\"https://www.mountainproject.com/area/113228283/picnic-area-boulders\">Picnic Area Bou&hellip;</a>\n        \n             &gt; <a href=\"https://www.mountainproject.com/area/106522335/olympus-boulder\">Olympus Boulder</a>\n    <br>Shared By: Aaron Parlier",
